column5: Caught this fish trolling the Thames river Saturday. All the time I've put in chasing these fish finally paid off. Fish measured 48 inches personal best for me by far. I wish now I had taken a girth measurement to get a rough estimate of weight but releasing the fish was the only thing on my mind after a quick picture.
Look at the head on that fish!!!!! Congrats man, wicked catch!!!
Awesome fish man !!! Wow .... What a behemoth congrats on your new PB !!!!!
NICE.   Congrats on a great catch.
Nice fish, probably a 20" or 21" girth, 25-30 pounds.
Awesome fish, glad your persistence paid off.
Jezz Louise, that is all I can say!
Super nice fish. I think I might have even seen you catch it. Was there Friday, Saturday, Sunday in a Green Crestliner
Nice job !  Saw you on the weekend.  I was in the Green and white Crestliner.  JIm
Thanks guys. My buddy told me as I was unhooking the fish boats going by we're snapping pictures lol  believer and misty river how did you guys make out?

Thanks guys. My buddy told me as I was unhooking the fish boats going by we're snapping pictures lol believer and misty river how did you guys make out?  We ended up getting 5 for the weekend.  46, 42, 41, 40 and a 38.
